<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="HappyFlower" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="12" />抱歉突然叫住你，<delay frames="40" />
因為<delay8 />我有件事<delay20 />
無論如何都想跟你說<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道表情是什麼嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就像這樣，<delay20 />
配合當下的心情來活動身體～<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當你想做表情的時候，要按下<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />喔。<10_4 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="16" />別忘了選擇<delay8 />
你想表達的心情，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />另外還有各式各樣的表情，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也會去教<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="8" />的其他人<delay20 />
如何使用喔。</message>
	<message label="Grin" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我跟你說一件好事！<10_4 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當你想向別人傳達心情時，<delay20 />
有一種表情可以讓自己提起勇氣喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你在我的心目中是最棒的！<10_4 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使在你的心目中，<delay8 />
我並非第一也一樣<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你想傳達心情時，<delay20 />
就像這樣使用這個「微笑」吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定會讓你勇氣百倍喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="OhGeez" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我跟你說一件好事！<10_4 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當你想向別人表達鬱悶的心情時，<delay20 />
有種表情很適合喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="20" />收到這麼多的<delay8 />情人節巧克力，<delay20 />
但我一個人吃不完啦～<colour id="4" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="65535" />你想傳達心情時，<delay20 />
就像這樣使用這個「算了」吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />或許會獲得其他人的共鳴喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="BrokenHeart" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我跟你說一件好事！<10_4 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比如說你覺得傷心的時候，<delay20 />
有種表情能鼓舞精神喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你說什麼！？<10_4 />
<anim id="BrokenHeart" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="30" />這樣啊<tag a="110" b="0" />不過，<delay20 />
