就像這樣使用這個「心碎」吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />或許能轉換心情喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="Sleep" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我跟你說一件好事！<10_4 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有種表情能夠表現出<delay8 />
有點疲憊的樣子喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要稍微休息一下就沒事了……<delay frames="40" />
