<anim id="Sleep" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="5" />呼<tag a="110" b="0" /><colour id="65535" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你想稍微休息一下時，<delay20 />
